WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
[Lisa] Hello everyone, my name is Lisa Miller.

00:04.000 --> 00:06.120
[Lisa] I am 25 years old.

00:06.120 --> 00:07.840
[Lisa] I am from Germany.

00:07.840 --> 00:09.400
[Lisa] I am a nurse.

00:09.400 --> 00:12.520
[Lisa] I work in a big hospital in Berlin.

00:12.520 --> 00:16.560
[Lisa] I help sick people and talk to doctors every day.

00:16.560 --> 00:17.960
[Tom] Hi Lisa.

00:17.960 --> 00:19.600
[Tom] I am Tom Wilson.

00:19.600 --> 00:21.440
[Tom] I am 28 years old.

00:21.440 --> 00:23.480
[Tom] I am from Canada.

00:23.480 --> 00:26.640
[Tom] But now, I live in France.

00:26.640 --> 00:28.760
[Tom] I am a chef.

00:28.760 --> 00:31.280
[Tom] I work in a small French restaurant.

00:31.280 --> 00:36.720
[Tom] I cook delicious food and bake fresh bread every morning.

00:36.720 --> 00:39.960
[Ali] Hello, my name is Ali Hassan.

00:39.960 --> 00:42.160
[Ali] I am 31 years old.

00:42.160 --> 00:44.240
[Ali] I am from Egypt.

00:44.240 --> 00:47.000
[Ali] I live in a sunny city near the sea.

00:47.000 --> 00:50.520
[Ali] I am an IT specialist.

00:50.520 --> 00:53.080
[Ali] I work at home in my office.

00:53.080 --> 00:56.320
[Ali] I have a big desk and a very fast computer.

00:56.320 --> 00:58.720
[Lisa] Ali, tell us about your home.

00:58.880 --> 01:02.680
[Ali] I live in the city of Giza.

01:02.680 --> 01:05.240
[Lisa] Do you live alone in your house?

01:05.240 --> 01:07.480
[Ali] No, I do not.

01:07.480 --> 01:10.480
[Ali] I live with my wife and our two children.

01:10.480 --> 01:12.760
[Ali] We have a son and a daughter.

01:12.760 --> 01:14.880
[Ali] We live in a modern house.

01:14.880 --> 01:17.600
[Ali] It has three bedrooms, a big kitchen

01:17.600 --> 01:21.280
[Ali] and a beautiful balcony with flowers.

01:21.280 --> 01:22.960
[Tom] That sounds nice.

01:22.960 --> 01:27.080
[Tom] Lisa, do you have brothers or sisters in Germany?

01:27.160 --> 01:29.560
[Lisa] Yes, I have one brother.

01:29.560 --> 01:33.160
[Lisa] His name is Hans.

01:33.160 --> 01:35.880
[Lisa] He is a student at the university.

01:35.880 --> 01:38.120
[Lisa] He lives in a small flat.

01:38.120 --> 01:41.000
[Lisa] My parents live in a quiet village.

01:41.000 --> 01:44.920
[Lisa] They have a garden, a cat and a big dog.

01:44.920 --> 01:47.960
[Lisa] Tom, what about your family?

01:47.960 --> 01:50.560
[Tom] My family lives in Canada.

01:50.560 --> 01:52.120
[Tom] I have a sister.

01:52.120 --> 01:54.640
[Tom] She is a doctor in a clinic.

01:54.640 --> 01:56.320
[Tom] We are very close.

01:56.320 --> 01:58.680
[Tom] We talk on the phone every weekend.

01:58.680 --> 02:01.680
[Ali] Tom, tell us about your daily routine.

02:01.680 --> 02:05.520
[Ali] You are a chef, so you are very busy.

02:05.520 --> 02:08.920
[Tom] Yes, I get up very late at 11 o'clock.

02:08.920 --> 02:11.920
[Tom] I have a big breakfast and drink juice.

02:11.920 --> 02:15.040
[Tom] I go to the restaurant at 2 o'clock in the afternoon.

02:15.040 --> 02:18.080
[Tom] I work all evening and cook for many people.

02:18.080 --> 02:20.320
[Tom] I come home at midnight.

02:20.320 --> 02:23.920
[Tom] I am very tired, but I love my job.

02:23.920 --> 02:25.760
[Lisa] My day is different.

02:25.760 --> 02:28.080
[Lisa] I get up very early at 6 o'clock.

02:28.080 --> 02:31.120
[Lisa] I drink green tea and eat toast.

02:31.120 --> 02:33.200
[Lisa] I walk to the hospital.

02:33.200 --> 02:37.120
[Lisa] I work for eight hours.

02:37.120 --> 02:41.440
[Lisa] I help people and drink a lot of water.

02:41.440 --> 02:43.200
[Ali] I get up at 8 o'clock.

02:43.200 --> 02:45.640
[Ali] I help my children with breakfast.

02:45.640 --> 02:48.960
[Ali] Then I work on my computer and write emails.

02:48.960 --> 02:51.880
[Ali] At 1 o'clock, I have lunch with my family.

02:51.880 --> 02:56.120
[Ali] In the afternoon, I go to the gym or walk in the park.

02:56.120 --> 02:58.080
[Tom] What is your favorite food?

02:58.080 --> 03:00.520
[Tom] Do you like to eat in restaurants?

03:00.520 --> 03:03.000
[Lisa] I like healthy food.

03:03.000 --> 03:07.240
[Lisa] I eat a lot of fruit, vegetables and chicken.

03:07.240 --> 03:09.600
[Lisa] I drink water and orange juice.

03:09.600 --> 03:12.320
[Lisa] I do not like fast food.

03:12.320 --> 03:15.320
[Ali] I love traditional food from Egypt.

03:15.320 --> 03:18.520
[Ali] I like rice, beans and meat.

03:18.520 --> 03:21.120
[Ali] I also like very sweet coffee.

03:21.120 --> 03:23.360
[Ali] My wife is a great cook.

03:23.360 --> 03:26.080
[Tom] I love cheese and red wine.

03:26.080 --> 03:29.880
[Tom] My favorite food is pasta with seafood.

03:29.880 --> 03:31.880
[Tom] It is very tasty.

03:31.880 --> 03:34.680
[Tom] I also like chocolate cake and tea.

03:34.680 --> 03:38.760
[Lisa] What do you do for fun in your free time?

03:38.760 --> 03:40.200
[Ali] I like sports.

03:40.200 --> 03:43.280
[Ali] I play football with my friends on Saturdays.

03:43.280 --> 03:47.000
[Ali] Sometimes I watch films with my wife in the evening.

03:47.000 --> 03:48.480
[Tom] I love music.

03:48.480 --> 03:51.360
[Tom] I go to concerts or listen to the radio.

03:51.360 --> 03:54.960
[Tom] I also like to travel and see new cities.

03:54.960 --> 03:57.400
[Lisa] I like books and photography.

03:57.400 --> 04:01.800
[Lisa] I take many pictures of flowers and old buildings.

04:01.800 --> 04:03.760
[Ali] It was great to talk to you.

04:03.760 --> 04:06.240
[Ali] You are very interesting people.

04:06.240 --> 04:07.760
[Tom] I agree.

04:07.760 --> 04:10.080
[Tom] Have a nice evening, everyone.

04:10.080 --> 04:11.080
[Lisa] Goodbye.

04:11.080 --> 04:12.920
[Tom] See you soon.

04:12.920 --> 04:13.800
[Ali] See you soon.
